thumb.title: [Vocaloid/TuneLab Cover] Suburbia [Sonika]
thumb.description: This was a pain to make since the key signature changes at the end. TuneLab wouldn't let me change the key, so I had to manually edit Sonika's vocals in Mixcraft to get her in tune. If she sounds a little weird at the end, I'm sorry. I tried my best :( CREDITS: Suburbia - The Pet Shop Boys Sonika - Zero-G Samples Image - Me Midi - bettyloumusic.com/suburbiapetshopboys.htm Copyright Disclaimer: - Under Section 107 of the Copyright Act 1976, allowance is made for FAIR USE for purposes such as criticism, comment, news reporting, teaching, scholarship and research.
